caption.p: SimPlot analysis was used to plot the degree of similarity between the HPeV5 G001-19 sequence and those of the closest near-full length sequences of HPeV5 (AM235749 [ 16]) and HPeV3 (KY556671 [ 4]) available in NCBI. The position of the 5’UTR, viral peptides and 3’UTR are shown below the plot.
